===Verb===
'''fixed'''
# Past tense of ''to [[fix]].''
# [[Repair]]ed. 
#:''Has your car been '''fixed''' yet?''
# {{euphemism}} Of an [[animal]], [[spayed]] or [[neutered]].
# Of a [[gambling]] device or game, [[crooked]], [[dishonest]], or [[rigged]].
#:''Don't go to that [[casino]], the roulette wheel is '''fixed.'''''
# {{slang}} [[Attack]]ed or [[punish]]ed.  
#:''When we find out who squealed on our [[roulette]] wheel, they're going to get '''fixed'''.''
# {{slang}} Protected from [[arrest]].  
#:''Don't worry about it, we're '''fixed''' with the [[cop]]s.''
# Of a a public [[election]], [[rigged]] or [[altered]].


